description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 61, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 305, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 1 for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10615-51610-1.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [305 Votes, Hall of Fame]
